  <section class="scroll-reveal section-scanline relative overflow-hidden border-t border-surface-800 bg-surface-900 px-6 py-24 sm:py-32" data-reveal="fade">
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-3xl">
        ¿Listo para proteger tu servidor?
      </h2>
      <a href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1038186932456390726&permissions=277025745990&scope=bot+applications.commands&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fthreat-bot-discord.vercel.app%2Fthanks&response_type=code" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group cta-primary inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-discord px-10 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">
        <Icon name="plus" />
        Añadir a Discord
